# 📱 DUOGRIND

> Study together. Focus harder.

DUOGRIND is a mobile-first study session app designed to help students overcome procrastination through short, structured focus sessions and light competition.
## 🎯 Why the name DUOGRIND?

- "Duo" represents accountability and competition
- "Grind" represents focused effort and discipline

Together, DUOGRIND captures the core idea:
Studying with pressure, structure, and consistency.
